{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_119","type":"agent_message","text":"The underlying build issue is in shared test build logic, not PostgreSQL itself. The GraalVM native plugin registers `build/test-results/<task>/testlist` as a tracked output directory, and with Gradle 9 that volatile per-run file set trips state tracking; I’m disabling state tracking for the shared `test` task with a narrow reason string."}}
